<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Teaching to You</title>
    <link href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Hanken Grotesk' rel='stylesheet'>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.4/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Hanken Grotesk';
            font-size: 22px;
            position: relative; /* Ensure relative positioning for absolute children */
        }
        .navbar {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); /* Transparent black background */
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            position: absolute; /* Position the navbar */
            width: calc(100% - 200px); /* Occupy full width minus the width of the person icon */
            top: 0; /* Position at the top */
            left: 0; /* Align to the left */
            z-index: 1; /* Ensure it's on top of other elements */
        }
        .navbar a {
            color: white; /* Set link color to white */
            text-decoration: none; /* Remove underline from links */
            margin: 0 10px; /* Add some spacing between links */
        }
        .person-icon {
            position: absolute; /* Position the person icon */
            right: -125px; /* Adjust the distance from the right edge */
            top: 23px; /* Adjust the distance from the top edge */
        }
        .navbar .dropdown {
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .dropdown-content {
            display: none;
            position: absolute;
            background-color: #1B3D6D;
            min-width: 160px;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .dropdown-content a {
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: block;
        }
        .dropdown-content a:hover {
            background-color: #ddd;
            color: black;
        }
        .dropdown:hover .dropdown-content {
            display: block;
        }
        .container {
            position: relative;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }
        .background-image {
            background-image: url('https://images.pexels.com/photos/951382/pexels-photo-951382.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=2');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start; /* Align items to the start of the container */
            justify-content: center;
            flex-direction: column;
            padding: 50px; /* Add more padding for spacing */
            position: relative; /* Position the container relative to the parent */
        }
        .btn {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: darkblue;
            color: white;
            font-style: 'Hanken Grotesk';
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin: 0 10px; /* Add margin between buttons */
            text-decoration: none; /* Remove underline from buttons */
        }
        .button-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center; /* Center buttons horizontally */
        }
        h1 {
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 64px;
            margin-top: -15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px; /* Add margin bottom for spacing */
        }
        p {
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.5; /* Set line height for multiple lines */
            max-width: 600px; /* Set max width to limit text width */
            margin-bottom: 20px; /* Add margin bottom for spacing */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="navbar">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <div class="dropdown">
            <a href="#">Letters</a>
            <div class="dropdown-content">
                <a href="/newsletters">Newsletters</a>
                <a href="/letters">Writing a Letter</a>
                <a href="/upload">Upload Your Letter</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <a href="/opportunities">Opportunities</a>
        <a href="/about">About</a>
        <a href='/login'><i class="fas fa-user person-icon"></i></a> <!-- Font Awesome person icon -->
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="background-image">
            <h1>Teaching to You:<br>Politics, Voting,<br>and Advocacy</h1>
            <p>Empowering American teens to become civically involved, from writing letters to elected officials to learning about the upcoming election.</p>
            <div class="button-container">
                <a class="btn" href="/about">Learn More</a>
                <a class="btn" href="/register">Sign Up</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>


